GOAL_OF_THE_MONTH.notes: Fernandes rounded off a flowing Man Utd counter-attack with a volley at Brighton on 30 June.
The Portuguese secured his second Goal of the Month award with a curling effort for Man Utd against Everton.

PLAYER_OF_THE_MONTH.notes: A goal and two assists capped an impressive start to the Manchester United midfieler's Premier League career.
The Man Utd midfielder scored four goals to help him win back-to-back awards, becoming the seventh player to do so.
Four goals and an assist were enough to see Fernandes claim the award for the third time.
Three goals and four assists meant Fernandes became the first player to win the award four times in a calendar year.

GOAL_OF_THE_MONTH.notes: The Denmark midfielder scored with a 30-yard strike in Spurs' first PL victory at Chelsea on 1 April 2018.
